matter of science.

03:10.942 --> 03:12.068
What do we do?

03:12.151 --> 03:14.070
Well, since
Calculon killed himself,

03:14.153 --> 03:16.572
his disembodied
software is in limbo,

03:16.698 --> 03:19.117
running on
the computational cloud.

03:19.242 --> 03:22.036
