Leave me alone!

03:32.463 --> 03:33.631
(ROBOTS SCREAMING)

03:37.593 --> 03:38.720
Ow!

03:39.137 --> 03:40.138
Ow!

03:40.763 --> 03:44.517
O, tears! O, lamentations!

03:44.600 --> 03:48.062
Would that mine
eternal torment might cease!

03:48.146 --> 03:51.983
Oh! Will you shut up? You've
been talking for a solid year.

03:52.066 --> 03:55.570
You know, Hell used to be a
nice place before you got here.

