03:59.490 --> 04:00.575
(BOTH GRUNTING)

04:00.658 --> 04:02.452
Ah! These guys.

04:02.535 --> 04:05.663
That's right, Robot Devil, and
we've come to reclaim a soul.

04:05.747 --> 04:06.748
A what?

04:06.831 --> 04:09.584
You know, the disembodied
software, whatever.

04:09.667 --> 04:10.752
Oh!

04:10.835 --> 04:12.420
Then the answer is no.

04:12.503 --> 04:15.840
Once a robot comes here,
he's mine for all eternity.

04:15.923 --> 04:17.216
Now hit the bricks.

04:17.550 --> 04:20.887
(SIGHS) You heard him, Bender.
Calculon's gone forever.

04:20.970 --> 04:22.096
Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!

04:22.180 --> 04:24.015
Did you say Calculon?

04:24.098 --> 04:27.143
(CHUCKLES) Perhaps we can
make a deal of some sort.

04:27.518 --> 04:28.728
(LAUGHS)

04:29.771 --> 04:33.441
Hark! Is it possible the hour
of mine deliverance is nigh?

04:33.524 --> 04:36.110
Will you stop hamming
it up for one second?

04:36.194 --> 04:38.237
They can't see or hear you.

04:38.321 --> 04:39.322
Their loss.

04:39.405 --> 04:41.157
I propose a competition.

04:41.240 --> 04:44.702
If I win, we get Calculon.
lfl lose, you kill us.

