04:52.210 --> 04:53.211
Um...

04:53.586 --> 04:56.214
It's between one and three.
Four!

04:56.297 --> 04:57.840
Between one and three.

04:57.924 --> 04:59.759
Not including one or three.

04:59.842 --> 05:01.594
"M"!
Is he right?

05:01.677 --> 05:05.932
Yes. The number I was
thinking of was the letter

